snippet.title: Prepper Russ
snippet.description: On my Prepper Russ channel, I make informative and entertaining videos about every prepping and survival scenario you may encounter. From EDC bugout bags to power outage and blackout situations. I'm always working on new doomsday prepping videos, so please let me know if you have a suggestion for future content.
